snippet.textDisplay: There is plenty of blame to go around.  Djokovic was cleared for entry into Australian because of his exemption.  But when he landed in Australia he was not allowed in the country.  As one Judge said : "What more can this man do ?"  It seems there are two Australia's battling here : the legal one that let him in and the political one which wants him out.  The left hand does not know what the right hand is doing.  Ridiculous.  If I was to bet it would be that the Political Australia will win this one and Djokovic will not play in the Aussie Open.
